text: Lee Fu-hsiang (born 17 February 1960) is a Taiwanese former cyclist. He competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Taiwanese male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Taiwan Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
